COMPUTE SELECTION SORT OF ARRAY
    SET I TO 1
OUTER LOOP
    SET MIN-IDX TO I
    SET J TO I PLUS 1
INNER LOOP
    IF ARRAY(J) LESS THAN ARRAY(MIN-IDX) SET MIN-IDX TO J
    INCREMENT J
    IF J NOT GREATER THAN N GO TO INNER LOOP
    SWAP ARRAY(I) AND ARRAY(MIN-IDX)
    INCREMENT I
    IF I LESS THAN N GO TO OUTER LOOP
STOP
